replies.body:
Huh... I won...

I did NOT think that would happen.

That being said... yay! {{sticker:garen-swing}} 

Well, thanks for choosing me. There were a lot of great entries in my opinion ('Down the fog' and 'A Killer Performance' were my favorites). If you're still posting, feedback would be appreciated _a lot_ from any of you guys.

I just received my winner e-mail and I'm in the process of replying to it.

Thanks again so much. I love you guys {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
